How to use:
run aqib's stuff (add the add_to_backend.txt parts somewhere)
change the directory name in if __name__ == __main__ (you can unless you change stuff on aqib's stuff ignore the second value)
(just use ctrl+f to find stuff)
if fonts issue is thrown read the fixfonts issue thing or google


change animation process

control for process is in the values structure
(just ignore the nestedness I have that handled)
total is the amount of kms
phases are different animation logic things
    ignore range, that's just the frames of the sequence
    threshold is the ratio on which this phase starts
    cont is when the animation plays regardless of progress
    loops means the animation is looped, otherwise the animation just stops here
    color is the text color (keep in mind the order is blue,green,red for some reason)


controls:
if backend update too slow change value in time.sleep
if not backend running/additionally/time control
    k - move back (won't work on stuff where different phases exist)
    l - move front
video control video reset values not reset:
    a- switches to video before in directory(loops between indexes)
    d - switches to video before in directory(loops between indexes)
RESET VALUES TO 0 (already considers server values)
    r - reset values (use if switching to new)